        {
            "title": "中國據悉要求本地經紀公司將客戶伺服器遷出交易所數據中心",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 知情人士透露，中國正在取消高頻交易機構的一項核心優勢，要求將這些公司專用的<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:伺服器;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/伺服器\">伺服器</a>移出本地交易所的數據中心。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這些人士稱，上海和廣州的大宗商品期貨交易所已依照監管機構的指示，要求本地經紀公司將客戶伺服器遷出交易所運營的數據中心。這一措施影響的不僅僅是高頻交易機構，但它們受到的衝擊可能最大。知情人士稱，上海期貨交易所已通知經紀公司在下月底前撤走高頻交易客戶的設備，其他客戶則需在4月30日前完成遷移。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-ee60628e-b0f8-3f6d-a139-4ea0532d135a-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此次調整將影響中國本土的高頻交易機構，同時也會影響一批活躍在該市場的全球企業。知情人士表示，城堡證券、Jane Street Group和Jump Trading等外資公司也在受影響之列。因相關事項不公開，知情人士要求匿名。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/FPvasUX8zH4Myo0u2dDUvg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/vi/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/12038c89e9dce0258300a8dc6929123b\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">相關變動將威脅高頻交易機構和量化對沖基金長期以來用於擊敗競爭對手的速度優勢。通過將伺服器部署在交易所的自有數據中心，這些公司能比其他人獲得略快的交易執行速度——在每毫秒都至關重要的市場，這種優勢尤為關鍵。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">交易機構雖不直接將其伺服器放在交易所內，但可借助本地經紀公司實現，經紀公司通過提供此類服務來爭取業務。一位知情人士透露，一些中國經紀公司近日已將高頻交易客戶的伺服器遷出深圳證券交易所的數據中心。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國證監會和城堡證券的代表未回覆置評請求。Jane Street、Jump不予置評。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China Clamps Down on High-Speed Traders, Removing Data Servers</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%93%9A%E6%82%89%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E7%B6%93%E7%B4%80%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%B0%87%E5%AE%A2%E6%88%B6%E4%BC%BA%E6%9C%8D%E5%99%A8%E9%81%B7%E5%87%BA%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E6%89%80%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83-014200197.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-16 10:55:52",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "聯儲會理事Barr認為司法部調查是對央行獨立性的「攻擊」",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"聯儲會理事Barr認為司法部調查是對央行獨立性的「攻擊」\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/RKswiYa390hCjY0BYCXiGA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-01/b8eda360-f25c-11f0-ad3f-eadbad085ddc\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">聯儲會理事Barr認為司法部調查是對央行獨立性的「攻擊」</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%9B%85%E8%99%8E%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%A0%B1%E5%B0%8E%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E6%9C%83%E7%90%86%E4%BA%8Bbarr%E8%AA%8D%E7%82%BA%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E9%83%A8%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E6%98%AF%E5%B0%8D%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E6%80%A7%E7%9A%84-%E6%94%BB%E6%93%8A-173627500.html",
